body_html:
You can try googling for that Python error. It is definitely not unique to TensorFlow, and given that the package works for me on Ubuntu 14, it has to either be your Python or SSL configuration or your network. You can try downloading the file manually with wget and then pip installing afterwards.

i.e.

wget $TF_BINARY_URL
pip install <insert the filename that is downloaded>
